Sentencas: NdBa0.5Sr0.5CO2-xMnxO5+delta (x=0, 0.25, and 0.5) specimens are synthesized and investigated as cathode materials for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Effect of Mn on the electrochemical properties of a layered perovskite NdBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xMnxO5+δ (x=0, 0.25, and 0.5) for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The interaction between two different transition metals, Mn and Co, may affect the electronic conducting properties and electrochemical performance.
Titulo: Effect of Mn on the electrochemical properties of a layered perovskite NdBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xMnxO5+δ (x=0, 0.25, and 0.5) for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The substitution of Mn for Co lowers the thermal expansion coefficient (TEC) of Co-based materials by suppression of the spin state transition of Co3+ which might consequently improve the mechanical compatibility with the electrolyte.
Titulo: Effect of Mn on the electrochemical properties of a layered perovskite NdBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xMnxO5+δ (x=0, 0.25, and 0.5) for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrochemical performance, however, could be slightly degraded by trapping of the effective mobile charge with increasing Mn content.
Titulo: Effect of Mn on the electrochemical properties of a layered perovskite NdBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xMnxO5+δ (x=0, 0.25, and 0.5) for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Such a substitution of Co by Mn would provide a tradeoff relationship between TEC and electrochemical performance in IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Effect of Mn on the electrochemical properties of a layered perovskite NdBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xMnxO5+δ (x=0, 0.25, and 0.5) for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this paper, the tradeoff between electrochemical and thermal expansion is explored.
Titulo: Effect of Mn on the electrochemical properties of a layered perovskite NdBa0.5Sr0.5Co2-xMnxO5+δ (x=0, 0.25, and 0.5) for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
